title: Go Get My Lunch 2017
itunes:title: Go Get My Lunch 2017
description:
A room filled with heroes Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Colleen Wolfe, & Gregg Rosenthal,– recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Hurricane Irma watch, the Colts trading Dorsett for Brissett, and Andrew Luck out for week one.  In this special show, the heroes give you their predications for 2017 in a fan favorite game, Go Get My Lunch!
